{"title":"光荣的大胡子","authors":["张永枚"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的大胡子　（儿童诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张永枚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少年宫里飞彩旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎古巴的好战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人向我们直招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又摸摸脸上的大胡子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胡子呀黑亮亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象墨菊正开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胡子呀真坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海底的铁树一个样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人抱起小弟弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直叫亲爱的小乖乖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟弟摸着那大胡子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爷爷，您的胡子真可爱！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人的笑声震动屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻译阿姨也笑不住："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“客人今年才三十多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别喊爷爷叫叔叔！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“叔叔为啥有大胡子？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“胡子里头有故事！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们围着客人坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人就讲起那胡子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前古巴象地狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人无食又无衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬和庄园主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬把工农踩在地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎要伤人就打虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要得自由就革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个英雄卡斯特罗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导人民闹翻身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七枝步枪冲上山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上的日子似黄连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒蛇猛兽常出入，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺粮少弹又缺穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿山过林打游击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披星戴月去杀敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们每时每刻里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想的是赶走狗美帝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有工夫去刮脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子一天长一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象山上的林间地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼春草就长遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卡斯特罗胡子硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是古巴的美髯公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说亲爱的伙伴们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的胡子很光荣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子留的是英雄气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不到胜利决不剃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡子留的是大志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓把革命干到底……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胡子战士真英勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻城夺地打先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天是七枝步枪山一座，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到今天千军万马全国红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民热爱大胡子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编成歌曲来传颂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人害怕大胡子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬牙切齿失掉魂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听完故事看客人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客人的胡子更威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们挨个拥上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着那胡子亲一亲。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}